        f"Enabled:             {values[2]}\n"
        f"Last Logon:          {values[3]}\n"
        f"Password Last Set:   {values[4]}\n"
        f"Password Never Exp:  {values[5]}\n"
        f"Locked Out:          {values[6]}\n"
        f"Primary Group:       {values[7]}\n"
        f"Risk Flags:          {values[8]}\n"
        f"\nInvestigation notes:\n"
        f"- Verify account ownership with HR/manager if stale or disabled.\n"
        f"- Locked accounts may indicate brute-force activity — cross-reference Event ID 4625.\n"
        f"- Password-never-expires accounts should be reviewed per policy.\n"
        f"- Never-logged-in accounts should be disabled or removed if not expected."
    )
    messagebox.showinfo("AD Account Detail", detail)


